    <h1>LinkedIn Document Post</h1>
    <p class="description">A native LinkedIn format that displays a multi-page PDF as a <strong>swipeable carousel</strong> inside the feed. Document posts generate more dwell time than any other LinkedIn format — which translates directly to algorithmic reach.</p>
